quran[75]{c,v,t}:
  87,1,Lemekeza dzina la Ambuye wako wapamwambamwamba
  87,2,Amene adalenga zonse ndi kuzikonza bwinobwino
  87,3,Amene adalamula tsogolo lawo ndi kuwatsogolera
  87,4,Amene amameretsa msipu
  87,5,Ndipo amausanduliza kukhala udzu ouma
  87,6,Tidzakuphunzitsa kulakatula chivumbulutso chathu ndipo sudzaiwala
  87,7,Kupatula chokhacho chimene Mulungu amafuna. Ndithudi Iye amadziwa chilichonse chooneka ndi chobisika
  87,8,"Ndipo Ife tidzakufupikitsira, m’njira yaifupi"
  87,9,Motero kumbutsa mwina chikumbutso chingawathandize
  87,10,Chikumbutso chidzalandiridwa ndi iye amene amaopa Mulungu
  87,11,Koma munthu wochimwa adzachisiya
  87,12,Amene adzaponyedwa mu ng’anjo yamoto ndi kulawa ululu wake
  87,13,Mmene iye sadzafa kapena kukhala ndi moyo
  87,14,Zoonadi iye amene adziyeretsa adzakhala wopambana
  87,15,Amene amakumbukira dzina la Ambuye wake ndipo amapemphera panthawi yake
  87,16,"Iyayi, koma inu mumasangalala ndi zinthu za m’moyo uno"
  87,17,Ndipo moyo umene uli nkudza ndi wabwino ndi wosatha
  87,18,Ndithudi! Zonsezi zidalembedwa mu Mabuku akale a Mulungu
  87,19,Mabuku a Abrahamu ndi Mose
  88,1,Kodi wamva za chinthu chachikulu chimene chili nkudza
  88,2,"Nkhope zina, patsiku limeneli, zidzachititsidwa manyazi"
  88,3,Pogwira ntchito zotopetsa
  88,4,Iwo adzalowa kumoto woyaka
  88,5,Iwo adzapatsidwa madzi oti amwe kuchokera kuchitsime cha moto
  88,6,Sadzakhala ndi chakudya china koma chiphe cha mtengo waminga
  88,7,Chimene sichidzawapatsa thanzi kapena kuthetsa njala
  88,8,"Nkhope zina, pa tsikuli, zidzakhala zosangalala"
  88,9,Adzakondwa chifukwa cha ntchito zawo
  88,10,Atakhala m’minda ya pamwamba
  88,11,Kumene iwo sadzamva zoononga kapena za bodza
  88,12,Mudzakhala kasupe wa madzi oyenda
  88,13,Ndi mipando yonyamuka ya wofowofo
  88,14,Ndi zikho zomwera zitaikidwa pambali pake
  88,15,Ndi makushoni yoikidwa m’mizere
  88,16,Ndi mikeka yoyalidwa bwino pansi pake
  88,17,Kodi iwo saona mmene ngamira zidalengedwera
  88,18,Ndi Kumwamba mmene kudakwezedwera
  88,19,Ndi mapiri mmene adalengedwera mokhazikika
  88,20,Ndi dziko mmene adalitambasulira
  88,21,"Motero akumbutse, chifukwa udindo wako ndi wowakumbutsa"
  88,22,Iwe sindiwe munthu wowakakamiza ayi
  88,23,"Kupatula iye Al Fajr\t651 amene abwerera m’mbuyo ndi kuyamba kusakhulupirira"
  88,24,Motero Mulungu adzamulanga chilango chachikulu
  88,25,Ndithudi onse adzabwerera kwa Ife
  88,26,"Ndipo, ndithudi, chiwerengero cha zochita zawo chidzakhala kwa Ife"
  89,1,Pali m’mbandakucha
  89,2,Ndi pali usiku khumi
  89,3,Pali chofanana ndi chosiyana
  89,4,Pali usiku pamene uli nkutha
  89,5,Ndithudi m’menemu muli umboni wokwanira kwa anthu a nzeru
  89,6,Kodi iwe siudaone mmene Ambuye wako adakhaulitsira anthu a Aad
  89,7,Amene anali atali atali ngati nsanamila zitali zitali
  89,8,wolingana nawo amene sanalengedwepo padziko
  89,9,"Ndi anthu a Thamoud, amene ankakumba nyumba zawo m’miyala ya m’dambo"
  89,10,"Ndi Farao, amene anali ndi zichiri"
  89,11,Amene anali kuphwanya malamulo paliponse m’dziko
  89,12,Ndipo adachulukitsa chisokonezo
  89,13,Motero Ambuye wako adabweretsa chilango chosiyana siyana chowawa pa iwo
  89,14,Ndithudi Ambuye wako amaona
  89,15,"Ndipo nthawi zonse munthu, pamene Ambuye wake amuyesa pomukweza ndi kumuonetsera chifundo chake, iye amati: “Ambuye wanga wandilemekeza ine.”"
  89,16,"Koma akamuyesa pomumana zinthu, iye amati: “Ambuye wanga ali kundizunza ine.”"
  89,17,Iyayi! Koma inu simuonetsa chifundo kwa ana a masiye
  89,18,Ndi kuuzana kuti mudzidyetsa anthu osauka
  89,19,Inu mumalanda chuma cha anthu opanda mphamvu chifukwa cha umbombo
  89,20,Ndipo mumakonda chuma ndi mitima yanu yonse
  89,21,Iyayi! Koma pamene dziko lidzasinjidwa kukhala ufa
  89,22,Ndipo Ambuye wanu adzadza pamodzi ndi angelo ali pa mizere
  89,23,"Ndipo Gahena idzabweretsedwa pafupi patsikuli. Ndipo patsikuli munthu adzakumbukira. Koma, kodi chikumbumtima chake chidzamuthandiza motani"
  89,24,"Iye adzanena kuti: “Kalanga ine! Ndikanakhala ndinali kuchita zabwino pamene ndinali ndi moyo.”"
  89,25,"Motero patsikuli, palibe wina amene adzalanga monga momwe Iye adzalangire"
  89,26,Ndipo palibe wina amene adzamanga monga ngati momwe Iye adzamangire
  89,27,oh! Iwe wokhutitsidwa
  89,28,"Bwerera kwa Ambuye wako mosangalala ndi Iye, ndi Iye mosangalala ndi iwe"
  89,29,Lowa m’gulu la akapolo anga wolemekezeka
  89,30,Ndipo lowa mu Paradiso yanga